<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="headerIcon">⚙️</view>
    <view class="headerContent">
      <view class="title">设置</view>
      <view class="subtitle">配置默认参数，提升使用效率</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="cardHeader">
      <view class="cardIcon">📦</view>
      <view class="cardTitle">压缩设置</view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认质量</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">按质量压缩时的默认值</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dragNumWrap">
        <view class="dragNumInner" bindtouchstart="onQualityTouchStart" bindtouchmove="onQualityTouchMove"
          bindtouchend="onQualityTouchEnd">
          <text class="dragNumValue">{{settings.compress.quality}}%</text>
          <text class="dragNumHint">← 滑动调整 →</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认目标大小</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">按大小压缩时的默认值</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dragNumWrap">
        <view class="dragNumInner" bindtouchstart="onTargetKBTouchStart" bindtouchmove="onTargetKBTouchMove"
          bindtouchend="onTargetKBTouchEnd">
          <text class="dragNumValue">{{settings.compress.targetKB}}KB</text>
          <text class="dragNumHint">← 滑动调整 →</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="cardHeader">
      <view class="cardIcon">💧</view>
      <view class="cardTitle">水印设置</view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认透明度</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">水印文字的默认透明度</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dragNumWrap">
        <view class="dragNumInner" bindtouchstart="onAlphaTouchStart" bindtouchmove="onAlphaTouchMove"
          bindtouchend="onAlphaTouchEnd">
          <text class="dragNumValue">{{settings.watermark.alpha}}%</text>
          <text class="dragNumHint">← 滑动调整 →</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认位置</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">水印显示的默认位置</text>
      </view>
      <view class="seg">
        <view class="segItem {{settings.watermark.position === 'br' ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onPositionChange"
          data-position="br">右下</view>
        <view class="segItem {{settings.watermark.position === 'bl' ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onPositionChange"
          data-position="bl">左下</view>
        <view class="segItem {{settings.watermark.position === 'tr' ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onPositionChange"
          data-position="tr">右上</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="cardHeader">
      <view class="cardIcon">📷</view>
      <view class="cardTitle">证件照设置</view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认规格</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">证件照的默认尺寸</text>
      </view>
      <view class="seg">
        <view class="segItem {{settings.idphoto.spec === '1' ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onSpecChange" data-spec="1">一寸
        </view>
        <view class="segItem {{settings.idphoto.spec === '2' ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onSpecChange" data-spec="2">二寸
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="settingItem">
      <view class="settingLabel">
        <text class="labelText">默认背景</text>
        <text class="labelDesc">证件照的默认背景色</text>
      </view>
      <view class="colorRow">
        <view class="colorItem {{settings.idphoto.bg === 'white' ? 'on' : ''}}"
          style="background: #FFFFFF; border: 2rpx solid #E5E7EB;" bindtap="onBgChange" data-bg="white">
          <view class="colorLabel">白底</view>
        </view>
        <view class="colorItem {{settings.idphoto.bg === 'blue' ? 'on' : ''}}"
          style="background: #4169E1; border: 2rpx solid #E5E7EB;" bindtap="onBgChange" data-bg="blue">
          <view class="colorLabel">蓝底</view>
        </view>
        <view class="colorItem {{settings.idphoto.bg === 'red' ? 'on' : ''}}"
          style="background: #CD5C5C; border: 2rpx solid #E5E7EB;" bindtap="onBgChange" data-bg="red">
          <view class="colorLabel">红底</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tipsCard">
    <view class="tipsHeader">
      <view class="tipsIcon">💡</view>
      <view class="tipsTitle">小提示</view>
    </view>
    <view class="tipsContent">
      <view class="tipsLine">
        <view class="tipsDot"></view>
        <text>这些设置只影响新创建的任务</text>
      </view>
      <view class="tipsLine">
        <view class="tipsDot"></view>
        <text>不会修改已保存的历史记录</text>
      </view>
      <view class="tipsLine">
        <view class="tipsDot"></view>
        <text>设置会自动保存，下次打开仍然有效</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text class="footerText">图像工具箱 v1.0.0</text>
  </view>
</view>